          Skills
          <span class="mobile-nav-indicator absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-500 to-green-500 transform transition-all duration-300 scale-y-0 opacity-0"></span>
        </a>
        <a href="#certifications" class="mobile-nav-link relative block w-full text-left px-3 py-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-cyan-400 hover:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-md transition-all duration-300" data-section="certifications">
